content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1220.73 - Excess valuation of parcels not to exceed $200 on any one parcel

State Regulations

Excess valuation shall not exceed $200 on any one
parcel. Port Authority liability for loss of, or damage to, or failure to
deliver a parcel shall not exceed the declared value thereof and in no event
shall exceed $225. Notes
